Version 1rc2 - released 2015-03-07
* lifted requirements to PHP >= 5.1.2
* improved JavaScript to suppport also older browsers (such as IE8)
* added support for "integrated" plugin menu

Version 1rc1 - released 2014-03-18
* fixed bug, where an img tag was missing the < (reported by learnandcode)

Version 1beta2 - released 2014-02-03
* (hopefully) fixed non-reproducible bug, where attributes were not completely
  removed from pagedata (reported by snafu)
* lifted requirements to PHP 5
* adapted for CMSimple_XH 1.6
* added CSRF protection (if available by CMSimple_XH)
* added German localization and manual
* added version.nfo
* improved QA: Phing, PHPCS, PHPCI, PHPUnit
* refactored to MVC architecture

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-02-26
* initial release
